query:
SELECT ce.id, ce.user_id, ce.course_id, c.title, ce.payment_status, ce.enrolled_at 
FROM course_enrollments ce 
LEFT JOIN courses c ON ce.course_id = c.id 
ORDER BY ce.user_id, ce.course_id, ce.enrolled_at DESC 
LIMIT 30;
